nodes.text: The Conjenus system was a star system that was located within the Vish sector, a part of the galactic regions known as the Mid Rim and the Trailing Sectors. It was home to the sentient Conjeni species.
The Conjenus system was established in the StarWars.com Online Companion to the 2009 reference book The Essential Atlas, which placed the system in grid square N-16.
